'''默基特希臘禮天主教聖保羅天堂之母教區'''（{{lang-la|Eparchia Dominae Nostrae Paradisis S. Pauli Graecorum Melkitarum}}；{{lang-pt|Eparquia de Nossa Senhora do Paraíso em São Paulo}}）是一個位於[[巴西|巴西]]的[[東儀天主教|東儀天主教]][[教區|教區]]（[[馬龍尼禮教會|馬龍尼禮教會]]），屬[[天主教聖保羅總教區|聖保羅總教區]]。

教區成立於1971年11月29日（自[[天主教巴西東方禮教長區|巴西東方禮教長區]]），<ref>{{cite web |title=DOMINAE NOSTRAE PARADISI* |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/paul-vi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_p-vi_apc_19711129_dominae-nostrae-paradisi.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2019-08-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190819171440/https://w2.vatican.va/content/paul-vi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_p-vi_apc_19711129_dominae-nostrae-paradisi.html |archivedate=2019-08-19 |language=la |date=1971-11-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2009年有420,000名教友、十三名司鐸、五個堂區。現任教區主教為{{link-en|喬治·克奧里 (主教)|George Khoury (bishop)|喬治·克奧里}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 17.06.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/06/17/190617b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-08-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190819163124/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/06/17/190617b.html |archivedate=2019-08-19 |language=en |date=2019-06-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-en|法里斯·馬卡倫|Fares Maakaroun}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e nomine, 21.07.2014 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2014/07/21/0528/01173.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-08-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190819174101/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2014/07/21/0528/01173.html |archivedate=2019-08-19 |language=it |date=2014-07-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

